abilities.description: (PASSIVE)WE ARE MORENaafiri spawns packmates that attack the targets of her attacks and abilities.
abilities.name: WE ARE MOREN

abilities.description: (Q)DARKIN DAGGERSNaafiri hurls up to two daggers, each inflicting bleed, or each inflicting bonus damage if the target is already bleeding. Packmates leap to attack champions hit by this skill.
abilities.name: DARKIN DAGGERSN

abilities.description: (W)HOUNDS' PURSUITNaafiri and her packmates dash at an enemy, colliding with the first champion hit and dealing damage.
abilities.name: HOUNDS

abilities.description: (E)EVISCERATENaafiri dashes and damages enemies in an area around her, recalling her packmates and fully healing them.
abilities.name: EVISCERATEN

abilities.description: (R)THE CALL OF THE PACKNaafiri empowers her pack and spawns additional packmates, instantly receiving a burst of speed and vision and gaining a shield the first time she hits another champion. After killing another champion for the first time, all effects are refreshed.
abilities.name: THE CALL OF THE PACKN
